reviews.review_text: Trippidy doo daa day!! Very nice sound to this! Hats off to Jay.The Bird song is off the hook and completely TRIPPY! Gives me goosebumps> listen for the Bird calls..I'm a fan of the Summer and Fall of 85' This show is short and sweet..I love the Scarlet Begonias minus the Fire..SMOKIN!! 2nd set is tight and well played and ends with a nice Morning Dew..so please>GIVE IT A WHIRL..Forever Grateful>Forever Dead!!!!!!!

primo second set fantastic 2nd set; jerry leads out from scarlet>touch of grey and never looks back. 2nd set board mix superior to 1st set w/ bobby and phil somewhat prominent. vip to drummers all night.

They are never gonna miss us... A good snapshot of why we gave up the Day Jobs and hit the road with the Boys. (Even though Jerry warned us not to)
This folks is just a perfect sounding show.
